{"name":"Alberta de Genne","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"Halfling","alignment":"nice","hitDice":"3","armorName":"leather armor","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"13 (leather armor)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":true,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"53 (10d8 + 8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"7","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"11","intPoints":"15","wisPoints":"16","chaPoints":"14","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"11","customCr":"1/2 (100 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The scout can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The scout regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the scout can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the scout can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The scout can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the scout's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the scout's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the scout dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Halfling","desc":"**Brave:** adv against fear. **Nimble:** move through creature's spaces. **Lucky** (maybe) **Squat Nimbleness:** adv against grapple"},{"name":"Archaelolgist","desc":"[Mon] is proficient with cartographer's tools and thieves' tools"},{"name":"Evasion","desc":"When [MON] succeeds a dexterity saving throw against a damaging effect she instead takes no damage, if she fails she only takes half damage."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"The [MON] is a 4th-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC [WIS SAVE], [WIS ATK] to hit with spell attacks). The [MON] has the following druid spells prepared:\n\n> Cantrips (at will): _Druidcraft, Mold Earth, Shape Water, Mending_\n> 1st level (5 slots): _Entangle, Cure Wounds, Healing Word, Goodberry, Longstrider_\n> 2nd level (4 slots): _Spike Growth, Animal Messenger, Lesser Restoration, Dakrvision_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Shortbow","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] piercing damage plus [4d6] piercing damage with **sneak attack.**"},{"name":"Shortsword","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] shashing damage plus [4d6] slashing damage with **sneak attack.**"},{"name":"Wild Shape (1/SR)","desc":"[Mon] polymorphs into a beast with CR 1/2 or lower (and no fly speed).\n\n[MON] can stay in beast form for **2 hours** but automatically reverts if she falls unconscious or dies.\n\nWhile polymorphed, [Mon] retains all of her abilities except her physical stats are replaced by the beasts and she cannot spellcast."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Cunning Action","desc":"[Mon] can take a Dash, Disengage, or Hide action."},{"name":"Spirit Totem (1/SR)","desc":"[Mon] summons an _incorporeal_ unicorn spirit at a point within 60 feet.\n\nThe spirit creates an aura in a 30-foot radius around that point. While the spirit is active [Mon] and her allies gain advantage on all ability checks made to detect creatures in the spirit’s aura. Additionally, when [Mon] casts a spell using a spell slot that restores hit points to any creature inside or outside the aura, each creature of your choice in the aura also regains **4** hit points.\n\nThe spirit lasts for **1 minute** and, as a bonus action, [MON] can move the spirit up to 60 feet to a point she can see."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Skirmisher","desc":"When an enemy end its turn within 5ft of [Mon], she can use her rection to move up to half her speed without taking opportunity attacks."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"dex","order":1},{"name":"int","order":3}],"skills":[{"name":"animal Handling","stat":"wis"},{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"nature","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"survival","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Druidic","speaks":true},{"name":"Halfling","speaks":true},{"name":"Sylvan","speaks":true},{"name":"Thieves' Cant","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Alberta","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":4,"damage":[]}